  "overview-limit": "<li data-section-id=\"1mwozmu\" data-start=\"17\" data-end=\"191\"><strong data-start=\"19\" data-end=\"44\">Objective understood:</strong> Develop a <strong data-start=\"55\" data-end=\"100\">360° full-body dermatology imaging system</strong> for <strong data-start=\"105\" data-end=\"190\">high-quality skin imaging, longitudinal lesion tracking, and AI-assisted analysis</strong>.<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"PDq2pG_selectionAnchor\"></span>\n</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"19c6qx6\" data-start=\"192\" data-end=\"337\">The system should provide <strong data-start=\"220\" data-end=\"310\">consistent image quality, accurate color reproduction, and comprehensive body coverage</strong> suitable for clinical use.</li>",
